"It is kinda funny how two different staples of the horror genre (the vampire and the mad scientist/monster combo) both have their origins in the horrifying experience of being trapped in a cabin with Lord Byron." - theaudientvoid

A ruby script to play Oliver Dakshire's one page solo roleplaying game, "Trapped in a Cabin with Lord Byron."

Find the original game here: 
https://twitter.com/Sotherans/status/1507670651724873730?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw


